1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object detection in images, which is a core topic in computer vision. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel approach for object detection using deep learning techniques. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses supervised learning techniques for training the model. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is possible as the paper discusses the challenges of detecting objects in aerial images, which is relevant to robotics applications such as drone navigation. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper deals with object detection in various types of images, including natural images, remote sensing images, and scene text data.
